    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014it runs super smooth and has been well-maintained over the years. The interior is nice and clean, and it\u2019s totally ready to hit the road for its next big adventure! It\u2019s perfect if you\u2019re looking for something reliable that still looks great. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
