    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This F87 M2 is a driver-focused example featuring the N55B30T0 3.0L twin-scroll turbocharged inline-six. The powertrain is mated to a 6-speed manual gearbox with an optimized throw, delivering power to the rear wheels via an electronically controlled Active M Differential. The suspension geometry utilizes lightweight aluminum control arms and stiffened subframe bushings for precise lateral turn-in. Recent preventative maintenance includes a high-pressure fuel pump inspection and a walnut blasting of the intake valves to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. Though the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including boost pressure consistency and oil analysis\u2014confirm a robust and well-sorted performance machine.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
