    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, showing only minor signs of road use such as light stone chips on the front bumper. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather upholstery has been regularly treated and remains supple, with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and navigation, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, benefiting from a strict adherence to its service schedule. Most recently, it has received a fresh synthetic oil change, new air filters, and a brake system inspection. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and provides a quiet, composed ride. This is a turn-key vehicle, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any deferred maintenance concerns.",
      "price": 35800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
